{{History||1.4.6|snap=12w50a|The Efficiency enchantment no longer applies when mining blocks of the wrong type (ex: Efficiency pickaxes don't increase the mining speed of dirt). This is a consequence of the new rule "the mining speed of a block is increased only when it is mined with the correct tool".}}
{{History||1.5|snap=13w09b|The proper tool now increases the breaking speed of a block even if it is not the correct grade.}}
